OL,3,CProperty body urges next government to
OL,4,Cup investment to boost affordable homes
OL,6,FA group of some of the UK's biggest
OL,7,Fconstruction companies has called on
OL,8,Fthe next government to pour up to an
OL,9,Fextra #14 billion into affordable
OL,10,Fhomes to ensure 145,000 are built
OL,11,Fevery year.
OL,13,FThe British Property Federation (BPF)
OL,14,Fhas called on whoever wins the next
OL,15,Felection to also ensure that around
OL,16,F30,000 build-to-rent properties are
OL,17,Fconstructed around the country.
