OL,3,CProperty body urges next government to
OL,4,Cup investment to boost affordable homes
OL,6,FMelanie Leech, the group's chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, said: "This year's election
OL,8,Fcomes at a critical time. The next
OL,9,Fgovernment must not only set out a
OL,10,Fcompelling vision for the future but
OL,11,Fwill need to persuade the electorate
OL,12,Fthat it can deliver."
OL,14,FIf the government works with industry
OL,15,Fit could unlock billions of pounds of
OL,16,Finvestment from property companies,
OL,17,Fthe BPF said as it unveiled its
OL,18,Fmanifesto ahead of the election.
