OL,3,CProperty body urges next government to
OL,4,Cup investment to boost affordable homes
OL,6,FIt said that #10 billion of new
OL,7,Fprivate capital could be unlocked if
OL,8,Fthe government increased subsidies for
OL,9,Faffordable housing by #9-#14 billion,
OL,10,Fadding that this could help deliver
OL,11,F145,000 new affordable homes every
OL,12,Fyear.
OL,14,F"As a country, we need to stimulate
OL,15,Feconomic growth and become more
OL,16,Fproductive," Ms Leech said.
