OL,3,CProperty body urges next government to
OL,4,Cup investment to boost affordable homes
OL,6,F"We need to invest billions of pounds
OL,7,Fin our infrastructure, our housing is
OL,8,Fof insufficient quantity and quality,
OL,9,Fand town centres across the UK need
OL,10,Freinvention.
OL,12,F"Looming over these issues is the
OL,13,Fexistential challenge facing all of us
OL,14,F` the need to decarbonise our society."
OL,16,FThe country is going to go to the
OL,17,Fpolls some time this year, or maybe in
OL,18,FJanuary 2025, if the Prime Minister
OL,19,Fholds out until the very latest
OL,20,Fpossible point.
