OL,3,CProperty body urges next government to
OL,4,Cup investment to boost affordable homes
OL,6,FThe BPF asked for government action in
OL,7,Fother areas, including building
OL,8,Fstronger town centres and trying to
OL,9,Fhelp developers erect greener
OL,10,Fbuildings.
OL,12,FIt should include more resources for
OL,13,Flocal planning officers, and a central
OL,14,Fplanning system which helps local and
OL,15,Fregional authorities with massive
OL,16,Fprojects, it added.
OL,18,FThe group also asked for reform to the
OL,19,Fbusiness rates system ` the business
OL,20,Fequivalent of council tax.
