OL,3,CProperty body urges next government to
OL,4,Cup investment to boost affordable homes
OL,6,FA Department for Levelling Up, Housing
OL,7,F& Communities spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fneed to build more affordable homes
OL,9,Fand that is why we continue to invest
OL,10,Fin our #11.5 billion Affordable Homes
OL,11,FProgramme, delivering tens of
OL,12,Fthousands of homes to buy and rent
OL,13,Facross the country.
OL,15,F"The Secretary of State recently set
OL,16,Fout new measures to speed up the
OL,17,Fplanning system and we remain on track
OL,18,Fto deliver one million homes over this
OL,19,FParliament.
